## Limitations

The analysis is based on available data and reports up to October 2023. The situation is dynamic, and factors influencing gas prices can change rapidly due to geopolitical events, policy changes, or unexpected disruptions in supply chains. Additionally, while the sources used are reputable, they may present information with inherent biases based on their editorial perspectives.